posts.title: Grok is still RETARDED 🤡

posts.raw_content:
We are witnessing what is about to become one of the most terrifying moments in history.  Several large players are aligning, with China, Russia and North Korea on one side, and the US, Japan, Korea and most of the southern pacific on the other.  China has deployed it's fleet provocatively in to Japan's waters, and Japan is publicly calling on the US to take a stand against this aggression.  The play is for Taiwan, and Japan has vowed to defend them.  Like I said a couple of years ago, watch for China to make a grab for the island it considers it's own.  But this time, instead of a fake pandemic that didn't work the way they planned, another more serious development has hastened China's urgency--AI or Artificial Intelligence.

You see, Taiwan is the largest producer of semiconductor chips in the world.  And the vast majority of them come to the United States.  Because of this, the US is beginning to widen it's lead in the field as companies like Google, Tesla and OpenAI are really starting to shine.  Specifically Tesla, which has most recently repeatedly widened it's lead with various versions of it's Grok AI.  And soon, when Tesla opens it's data center in Memphis, which will be wholly produced and powered by the company itself, with no adverse effects on surrounding neighbors like those who try to gaslight the world in believing, TeslaAI will become the defacto world leader in computing power by a wide margin. And with that also comes the AI.  The real prize here. Tesla, and the US, will win the race.  And yes, it is a race.  And every player KNOWS that whoever wins this race, wins it all.  The future, the governance, the influence, the power.  All of it. This IS the big one.  And they all know it.

Tesla's future is incredible.  If not inevitable--and this is a GOOD thing.  Why?  Because if Tesla, and to a certain extent Google do not succeed and try to win this race, China will.  And, as we have seen in their past, nothing good will come from this.  They will bully the world's population into submission as they are now in their own country.  Implement social credit systems as they are trying to throughout the world, including here in the US, through organizations like the WEF and unfortunately our political organizations, including both Democrats AND Republicans.  And as usual, instead of implementing true reforms that help all of humanity, communism, and it's twin brother socialism, will inevitably end up consolidating power to the very few. In Russia it is almost comical.  In North Korea...well, you see. And in China, masked as the will of the people, it is frightening.  Because China is rapidly approaching the US in world influence combined with military prowess.

If you don't think this is a valid scenario--ponder this:  Tesla with their SpaceX subsidiary, currently sends 90% of ALL payloads in the world. Every other entity, whether it be private or government, sends the other 10%.  That is staggering and incredibly relevant.  Because Elon has recently announced plans have his companies sending literally MILLIONS of rockets into space, all to build a giant power source AROUND THE SUN to harness this huge source--simply to power Tesla's AI.  And AI companies are in agreement:  To win the AI race, you MUST win the energy race.  And the ultimate energy source, by many factors, is the sun.  Which brings us to energy--specifically Venezuela.

Venezuela, the perfect example of failed socialism, just also happens to be the country with the largest known oil reserves in the world.  Yes, even bigger than Saudi Arabia.  And China and Russia have been developing this resource for a few years as the US has stood by idly.  The Biden administration was a DISASTER.  And we are feeling the effects now with runaway inflation and consolidation of power in South America from China and it's increasing relationship with Russia.  Socialists took over Brazil and Columbia with what were most likely fraudulent elections.  Very similar to the very first voting machine manipulation that originally brought Hugo Chavez into power in Venezuela, all instigated by an American company that eventually became Smartmatic, instigator of the 2020 fraud and those "81 million" votes Biden received.  Brazil just recently imprisoned Bolsonaro, their opposition candidate and now is solidly one party socialist rule. Columbia, once America's strongest ally in South America, also recently went socialist, with one party rule and no opposition.  Why do you think millions upon millions of illegal immigrants headed to the US?  Because we are the last bastion of freedom.  Something no other country in the world comes close. Belying the fact that China was readily instigating terror on the US by supplying the ingredients for the fentanyl crisis, along with encouraging millions of illegals to cross our borders to overwhelm our government and economic systems, their real intent is to get the chips for their AI, and to get the energy, alliances and disruptions from not only South American countries, but also Africa, the Middle East and the enigma in the room--Europe.  They too have become essentially socialists, and are rapidly become enemies of traditional western culture.  Like freedom of speech.  But recent actions by the US against Venezuela have very little to do with drugs.  It makes a convenient excuse.  It's ALL about AI and the control of the chips and the energy to power it.

Recently as we all know, the US moved and ENTIRE FLEET off the coast of Venezuela.  Why do we need this much firepower to stop drugs?  We don't.  They are there preparing.  Preparing for the invasion of Taiwan.  And when that happens, the US will take out ALL of the unjust regimes in this region.  Because if they don't, and a Pacific war begins between what will essentially be between the US with it's allies mentioned and China and it's allies which INCLUDES the most prolific NUCLEAR power in Russia, both of those countries have ALREADY committed to back Venezuela in any conflict.  It's about to get ugly.  And it's NOT going to be just in Taiwan and South America. You see, that stupid, dumb, illegitimate drug-induced "Resident" squatter we had for four horrible years in the white house allowed MILLIONS of fighting age men, from all over the world, to infiltrate all areas of our country.  Many, if not most, hold no allegiance to their new country.  They are just lying in wait.  Preparing for the opportunity they were sent here for.  To take over the richest, most free and best in the world.  They want EVERYTHING we have now.  And if we don't wise up, they will get it. Including our liberty if not our life.
